cat << EOF
KRadio is an AM/FM/Internet radio application for KDE4.
It has support for V4L and V4L2 radio devices, internet radio,
RDS, lirc remote control, MP3 and Ogg/Vorbis recording,
TimeShift playing, alarms and much more.
